Reimagining the Icon with Interactive SVGs

Billy Beer is back, and this time, it's tapping into the future! We're excited to unveil our brand refresh, featuring a suite of six interactive SVG icons that embody the essence of the Billy Beer experience.

What are SVGs?

SVG stands for Scalable Vector Graphics. These graphics are ultra-modern and lightweight, allowing for crisp visuals that adapt seamlessly to any screen size. But Billy Beer isn't about just looking good – it's about interactivity!
